"F[c];" "6#&%\"FG6#%\"cG" }{TEXT -1 102 " = Linear force produced by t
he motor at the motor pinion (i.e. after the gearbox): cart driving fo
rce" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {XPPEDIT 18 0 "F[c]" "6#&%\"FG6#%\"cG" }{TEXT 
-1 46 " is calculated in the Maple worksheet titled: " }{TEXT 263 20 "
