27 "They are symmetric in form." }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 101 "The i
nertia (a.k.a. mass) matrix, F, gives indications regarding the coupli
ng existing in the system." }}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 
